Bet winnam parahdijahs weens Engelis no Debbeſim / winnu eeſtiprinadams/ un kad winſch ar Nahwes Behdahm zihnijahs/ peeluhd⸗ ſe winſch DEewu jo karſtaki/ bet winna Sweedri bija kà Affins Lahſes/ tahs nokritte Semmê. Un winſch no tahs Peeluhgfchanas zehlees/ nahze peo faweem Mahzekleem/ un atradde tohs gullim no Noſkumfchanas/ un fazzija us teem: Ak! gribbat juhs nu gulleht un duffeht? Ko gullat juhs? Jaw gan irr/ redſi/ ta Stunda irr nahkuſi/ un ta Zilwe⸗ ka Dehls tohp nodohts Grehzineeku Rohkàs/ zek⸗ keetees/ eima: Redſi/ kas manni (ar wiltu) nodohd/ tas irr tuwu klaht/ bet luhdſeet DEewu/ ka juhs Kahrdinafchanâ ne eekrihtat.
